phpShop is a free PHP-based e-commerce application developed by Edikon?. phpShop allows you to setup an online store and manage all aspects of your online business by using a web browser.

phpShop was designed as a tool to offer easy customization and a standardized platform for development of e-commerce applications. Its use of open source technoligies allows for cross platform deployment using any operating system that support PHP.

phpShop is distributed under the General Public License (GPL). You can Download phpShop for free.

